We could implement simple ranking: check for royal flush, straight flush, four of a kind, full house, flush, straight, three of a kind, two pair, one pair, high card.

We need to detect straight: need to convert ranks to numeric values: A=14, 2=2,...10=10,J=11,Q=12,K=13. Also handle Ace low straight (A,2,3,4,5). We'll implement.

We'll need to parse each card string: rank part may be '10' or single char. We'll extract rank = card.slice(0,-1); suit = card.slice(-1).

We'll compute values.

